<paragraph id="C4EA222EC07C177A9AB5A4D65D279A3F" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Stielloses Leimkraut</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="DDA58A9E24258A1FECF3EA7B2CBC1843" pageId="null" pageNumber="787" type="description">
<paragraph id="8A179055523D33DE1DD68866AD9721A1" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="F63FE8F77A90DBC72526AB5595809800" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Silene" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="787" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="acaulis">
<emphasis id="73C4CE454887E66FAA9D87CB25E2F5E4" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">S. acaulis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 24) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<normalizedToken id="18013C86E59751BDA2AC6E02703A1592" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
3-6 mm lang; 
<emphasis id="DC5421D08C820E64F0CC16DFBAE38872" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<normalizedToken id="2CF5C8082EBBD8C7540AEFEE2107C9C7" originalValue="Blütenstiele" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Bluetenstiele</normalizedToken>
kaum 
<normalizedToken id="6DA75DCDDA507725F1EB2AA749D65FC2" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">ueber</normalizedToken>
0,5 cm lang, etwas 
<normalizedToken id="BEFA249724234F4C8AE8D980BC618E54" originalValue="geflügelt" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">gefluegelt</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Kelch 3,5-6 mm lang, 
<emphasis id="3A0574C4D76A9A46C30D7382E6A4973D" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
am Grunde 
<normalizedToken id="EBBF7A6590A418AAF08FAD7A67B1A33A" originalValue="allmählich" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">allmaehlich</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
<emphasis id="146B47F7B7920E84914DB5F08DFD585E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<pageBreakToken id="92B39E5E80D87A15DFA487774438D1E8" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<normalizedToken id="ED6193D63D52ECC2FE00330CD8492621" originalValue="verschmälert" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">verschmaelert</normalizedToken>
</pageBreakToken>
;
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="21ED15A9424D29FCD811BA902143E729" originalValue="Kronblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Kronblaetter</normalizedToken>
5-10 mm lang, 1,5-2 mm breit, hellpurpurn, fast ganzrandig bis wenig ausgerandet; 
<emphasis id="39321AD52319B40B2798519B8A6F13A8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
Kapsel 3-5 mm lang, kaum 
<normalizedToken id="A706400DC9C7BAE70222A12472C4BCD1" originalValue="länger" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">laenger</normalizedToken>
als der Kelch.
</emphasis>
- 
<normalizedToken id="A4A06FA139E3759EF43BF8CC216C3F32" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="08E22A426D96CAEAF5D82EC3492A4C33" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<emphasis id="9D0FFFC0CA7A51F873134D92B5BF2A4C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Zytologische Angaben. 2n = 24:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Tirol (als 
<taxonomicName id="8F76C91A210020893B70154047A2824F" pageId="null" pageNumber="787" rank="subSpecies" subSpecies="norica">
ssp. 
<emphasis id="711E3F92064A8FE0694AC3A7D3AEC84A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">norica</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
[Vierh.] O. Schwarz; Favarger 1965).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1E7A9E989DBF1E313A1C8DE3D599CED8" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<emphasis id="0EB518B794CAD6815FC2B33325545C03" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Standort.</emphasis>
Alpin. Lockere, steinige, offene, exponierte, kalkarme 
<normalizedToken id="C81509E4288F352B89F217C108A2A6EA" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Boeden</normalizedToken>
. Grate, Felsen, offene Rasen. 
<emphasis id="A38BFBD38A75537CC67BE4160B917DD6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Caricetum curvulae</emphasis>
(Kerner) Brockmann-Jerosch 1907.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="9C77C32ADDDA4114DE0FBC3D03A2748E" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<emphasis id="A51C36C2565CD60502B0BFD582C1E2E8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="DB6D4453B36FF4DBFBEEAA9FC85EAC05" originalValue="Westalpin-pyrenäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Westalpin-pyrenaeische</normalizedToken>
Pflanze:
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="05147024734928047CA71B2DF051BEB1" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Westalpen (
<normalizedToken id="ECE71FB09C4DC24774EE3BE0B850FFCD" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Silvretta). Verbreitungskarte von 
<normalizedToken id="972F6956E9782E3A0237C848B621D7C6" originalValue="Merxmüller" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Merxmueller</normalizedToken>
(1952). - Im Gebiet: Alpen, nicht 
<normalizedToken id="C56E857B7B89E4F51714AF9041D8EC74" originalValue="häufig" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">haeufig</normalizedToken>
(in den Nordalpen sehr selten).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="ED8B67C5EDE0986212FE6299A8BFA8ED" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">
<emphasis id="9B947943D34479E84A0032DF76C11527" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Siehe unter 
<taxonomicName id="3072E6B22C172A63EB4E0557C572276D" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Silene" kingdom="Plantae" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="null" pageNumber="787" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="acaulis">
<emphasis id="1354783C5CAFCC94CD0B02D289122A0A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="787">S. acaulis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 24).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
